### Send an email to the queue
POST http://localhost:3000/send-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "to": "user@example.com",
    "subject": "Welcome to our platform!",
    "body": "Hi there, thank you for signing up. We are glad to have you."
}

###

### Process the next email in the queue
GET http://localhost:3000/email/process
